name: Listened to Apple Macbook Air with M1 review / Apple will reduce App Store cut to 15 percent / end-to-end encryption for RCS in Android

content.html:
Walt Mossberg joins the show to discuss his experience with Apple’s Macbooks with the new M1 chip. Nilay, Dieter, Chris, and Dan discuss The Verge’s reviews of the computers.
